          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've been testing email marketing platforms for years, and AWeber keeps surprising me in the best way. If you've wondered ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "what AWeber is",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and whether it still holds up in 2025, the answer is a resounding yes—and it's better than ever.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AWeber just rolled out a wave of updates that make it one of the most complete platforms for creators, solopreneurs, and small teams. Whether you're sending your first newsletter or scaling to thousands of subscribers, these new features deserve your attention.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I'll walk you through everything that's new, why it matters, and exactly who should be using AWeber right now. Let's dive in.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What's New at AWeber in 2025",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AWeber has been in the email game for over 27 years—yes, they literally invented the autoresponder. But age hasn't slowed them down. Their 2025 updates prove they're still innovating at full speed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here are the standout new features:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Integrated Payment Pages",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can now sell products and services directly from AWeber without needing a separate checkout tool. Payment pages are built right into the platform, so your audience can go from reading your email to paying you in two clicks. No Zapier workarounds. No third-party cart systems. Just a clean path from email to sale.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This alone saves small business owners hours of setup and hundreds of dollars in extra subscriptions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smarter Automations with Visual Workflows",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AWeber rebuilt their automation engine from scratch. The new drag-and-drop workflow builder lets you map out customer journeys visually—think welcome sequences, abandoned cart reminders, post-purchase follow-ups, and re-engagement campaigns. You connect triggers, conditions, and actions by dragging lines between blocks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/aweber-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What I love: the logic is dead simple. You don't need a marketing degree to build sequences that actually convert. If you want to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "master AWeber's automation tips",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", the learning curve is genuinely short.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enhanced Landing Page Builder",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The landing page builder got a serious upgrade. New templates, better mobile responsiveness, and custom domain support mean you can spin up high-converting pages in minutes. Lead magnets, webinar registrations, product showcases—AWeber handles them all without you touching a single line of code.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Subject Line Suggestions",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Writer's block on subject lines? AWeber's new AI assistant suggests subject lines based on your email content and past performance data. It's not replacing your voice—it's giving you a running start. In my tests, the AI suggestions consistently outperformed my first drafts.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Deeper Analytics Dashboard",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The revamped analytics give you real-time data on opens, clicks, revenue per email, and subscriber growth. You can filter by campaign, segment, or date range and actually understand what's working without exporting spreadsheets.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
