        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "My Honest Take After Testing AWeber in 2025",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've used Mailchimp, ConvertKit, ActiveCampaign, and a handful of others. Each has strengths. But for small business owners and solo creators who want a platform that's powerful without being overwhelming, AWeber is my go-to recommendation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The 2025 updates—especially payment pages and the visual automation builder—close the gap with more expensive competitors. Combined with legendary deliverability and actual human support, AWeber offers a package that's hard to beat at its price point.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is it perfect? No tool is. But if you need a reliable, affordable email marketing platform that grows with your business and doesn't require a CS degree to operate, AWeber deserves a spot at the top of your list.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Give it 14 days. Send a few campaigns. Build an automation or two. I'm confident you'll see why AWeber has stayed relevant for nearly three decades.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
