        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What new features did AWeber add in 2025?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AWeber introduced integrated payment pages for selling directly from emails, a visual drag-and-drop automation builder, an enhanced landing page builder with custom domains, AI-powered subject line suggestions, and a revamped analytics dashboard with real-time revenue tracking.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is AWeber free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, AWeber offers a free plan for up to 500 subscribers that includes core email features, landing pages, and basic automations. No credit card is required to sign up, and paid plans start at $14.99/month for additional features and higher subscriber limits.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does AWeber compare to other email marketing platforms?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AWeber stands out for its 27+ years of email deliverability expertise, 24/7 live human support (including phone), and its unique Done For You service where their team builds your entire email system in 7 days. It's particularly strong for solo entrepreneurs and small businesses who want powerful features without a steep learning curve.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I sell products directly through AWeber emails?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. AWeber's new integrated payment pages let you add checkout functionality to your emails and landing pages without needing third-party tools like Shopify or Gumroad. Customers can purchase in just two clicks from your email.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
